WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.400
Don't call him soft. He's the only one protecting our family bravely.

2
00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:07.120
Dad, please, if you care about us, just calm down.

3
00:00:07.120 --> 00:00:13.779
I am being calm! Joking this town!

4
00:00:13.779 --> 00:00:16.980
Dad, please. I'll talk to Mark. Just hold tight for now.

5
00:00:16.980 --> 00:00:37.310
Lesser, John.

6
00:00:37.310 --> 00:00:41.710
So you want to help my family escape? Why? You know the risks.

7
00:00:41.710 --> 00:00:45.229
Because I made you marry Pietro, my friend.

